<i>noun</i>: 환장 [환ː장], 골몰 [골몰] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>환장 [환ː장]</dt><br>
<dd>1. going crazy; going mad; being out of one's mind</dd><br>
<dd>마음이나 행동이 정상이 아닌 듯한 상태가 됨.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which one's state of mind or behavior becomes abnormal.</dd><br>
<dd>2. obssession; mania; preoccupation</dd><br>
<dd>(속된 말로) 어떤 것에 지나치게 집착하거나 집중해서 정신을 못 차리는 상태가 됨.</dd><br>
<dd>(slang) A state of being so excessively obssessed with or concentrated on something that one loses one's reason.</dd><br>
<dt>골몰 [골몰]</dt><br>
<dd>preoccupation; absorption</dd><br>
<dd>한 가지 일이나 생각에만 집중함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of concentrating on only one thing or thought.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>